on.","<b>Vegetable potato cakes<b>: replace <b>⅓ of<b> the potatoes with vegetables (e.g. carrots, kohlrabi, cauliflower, courgettes etc.). Double the amount of starch and oat flakes. Season with ground mixed pepper and serve with a sour cream herb dip."],"basicInfo":["easy","45m","45m","4 portions"]}